Package: debsign-rs
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Sign Debian packages with GPG (Rust implementation)
 debsign-rs is a tool for signing Debian packages using GPG.
 Written in Rust using sequoia-openpgp for cryptographic operations.
 .
 Features:
  * Sign .deb files with detached GPG signatures
  * Verify existing signatures on .deb files
  * Support for ASCII-armored key files
  * Generates MD5, SHA1, and SHA256 checksums
